## Features Implemented

### Doctor Listing API

* GET /doctor
* Returns doctor details including:

  * Doctor ID
  * Full Name
  * Specialization
  * Experience
  * Consultation Fee
  * Availability Status

### Search & Filters

* Filter by specialization
* Search by doctor name (partial match)
* Availability filter

### Pagination

* Page and limit query parameters
* Default pagination support

### Doctor Profile API

* GET /doctor/:id
* Returns doctor details by ID

### Edge Cases Handled

* Invalid doctor ID
* Invalid pagination values
* Negative page/limit values
* Empty search results
* No doctors found
* Missing query parameters

### Database

* Sequelize migration created
* Seeder created with sample doctor data

### Testing

* APIs tested using Postman
